text: Gone Pone also Tat Ka Tho Gone Pone(; born 31 August) is one of most popular and Myanmar Academy Award winning Burmese actress and presenter. She won her first Best Supporting Actress Academy Award in 2015 . She has acted in over 50 films. ==Personal life== Gone married Myat Htun Shwe. ==Awards and nominations== {| border="2" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%" |- bgcolor="#B0C4DE" align="center" !
